<li>Williams, T. Harry. <i>Huey Long.</i> Knopf, 1969. (Winner of the 1970 <a href="/wiki/Pulitzer_Prize" title="Pulitzer Prize">Pulitzer Prize</a> and the <a href="/wiki/National_Book_Award" title="National Book Award">National Book Award</a>)</li>
</ul>
